### Generation Pipeline

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[Mood Selection] --> B[Prompt Generation]
    B --> C[AI Audio Generation]
    C --> D[Volume Normalization]
    D --> E[Fade In/Out]
    E --> F[Loop Optimization]
    F --> G[MP3 Export]
```

