## ğŸ“ Example Output

Generated files are saved to `./output/` by default:

```
output/
â”œâ”€â”€ fmag-forest_cafe-20241125_143022.mp3
â”œâ”€â”€ fmag-night_coding_lofi-20241125_144530.mp3
â””â”€â”€ fmag-ocean_meditation-20241125_150015.mp3
```

Each file is:
- **192kbps MP3** format
- **Loop-optimized** with crossfade
- **Volume normalized** to -16 LUFS
- **Fade in/out** (0.5 seconds each)

